{"tid":1861872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【比卡超秒殺黑警】黑警有權拘捕「網上造謠者」？黑警自己就係造謠者！","createTime":"2020-02-04T10:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T18:40:00.000Z","uid":138409,"like":264,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf9695bd948254720022a9a56516cd041ff3795","tid":1861872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UqZGprx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUqZGprx.jpg&h=efe2eec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2741940912585842&amp;set=a.125153000931326&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2741940912585842%26set%3Da.125153000931326%26type%3D3%26theater&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=52c30a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2741940912585842&amp;set=a.125153000931326&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n垃圾，又唔撚讀書非法拘捕<br />\n終審法院喺2014年的《香港特別行政區訴陳宥羲》案[1]講得好清楚，香港法例第228章 《簡易程序治罪條例》 第20條只規管經「電報、電話、無線電報或無線電話傳送」的訊息，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但並不適用於互聯網上發放的信息</span>。<br />\n市民就真係呼籲黑警喇，切勿曲解法律、發放虛假訊息，此等試圖令他人產生不必要憂慮並無理剝奪人身自由的行為實屬違法，更會為社會添煩添亂。大家應同心抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfa/2014/18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fcgi-bin%2Fsinodisp%2Feng%2Fhk%2Fcases%2Fhkcfa%2F2014%2F18.html&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=3e0ae476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfa/2014/18.html</a><br />\n[1] (2014) 17 HKCFAR 110 第91(2)段：'Section 20 of the Summary Offences Ordinance makes it an offence to send any message &ldquo;by telegraph, telephone, wireless telegraphy or wireless telephony which is grossly offensive or of an indecent, obscene or menacing character&rdquo;, <span style=\"color: gold;\">but the medium of the internet is not addressed by that provision.</span>'"},{"pid":"2c99dae379c13838dc553d25d2a53952e23ee8de","tid":1861872,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5590f3aceea67d73acac50092d87734a597aa403","tid":1861872,"uid":255637,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又高調拉 低調放"},{"pid":"d815f04f62cff880f3435781b0ec4d4824ecaff5","tid":1861872,"uid":136661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a523abe698f69d3abe9ebf954d29b55fd5c39ea7","tid":1861872,"uid":201678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:15.000Z","msg":"《請全港醫護人員三思！》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861855</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4ed9c93a9830bf62ab6ea63c9d4b6a589c6d77d","tid":1861872,"uid":126839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daac9aade603c77981ebb0d0757f8cd28f4ca11a","tid":1861872,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d57769d4628d8afafc58769b3c3609e69cabf48","tid":1861872,"uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗post<br />\n去洗版啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/photos/pb.960526577368640.-2207520000../2948448388576439/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?